subproject.description:
The project will support the implementation of the Rights of Persons with Disabilities in Belarus in accordance with International standards by:
1.Carrying out necessary preparations for ratification of the UN Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities by Belarus; 
2.Developing and testing a monitoring system of the situation of persons with disabilities and of their rehabilitation effectiveness; 
3.Informing state bodies, the general public and international community about the situation of PWD in Belarus; 
4.Elaborating recommendations aimed at improving national policies regarding PWD;
5.Strengthening understanding of the rights, needs and potential of PWD among state structures, media and the general public.
